## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

* Does not currently ingest BOSH VM metrics outside of the core CF deployment.
* Intended to monitor the foundation it is installed on only.
* This product is still under active deployment. Therefore some links to deep-dive screens may still be inactive. Please see [Known Issues](release-notes.html) for current status.
* Currently, only the Google Chrome browser is supported when accessing the product UI.
* If an earlier version of PCF Healthwatch is installed, it must be deleted before proceeding with the installation of the newer tile. The tile is not upgradable at this time.
* The installation process is complex; we are looking to address this in future versions, but still welcome feedback on this topic.

